OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FA BBC board member's position is being
OL,7,Fcalled into question, amid accusations
OL,8,Fof bias at the broadcaster.
OL,10,FSir Robbie Gibb served as director of
OL,11,Fcommunications for Theresa May when
OL,12,Fshe was in Downing Street before
OL,13,Fjoining the corporation's board in
OL,14,F2021.
OL,16,FHis appointment was met with criticism
OL,17,Fat the time and has since been
OL,18,Freignited after director-general Tim
OL,19,FDavie and BBC News CEO Deborah Turness
OL,20,Fboth announced their resignations over
OL,21,Fthe weekend.
