OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FIt follows claims that clips were
OL,7,Fspliced together in the documentary
OL,8,F'Trump: A Second Chance?' to make it
OL,9,Fappear he had told supporters he was
OL,10,Fgoing to walk to the US Capitol with
OL,11,Fthem to "fight like hell".
OL,13,FTwo political leaders have now
OL,14,Fquestioned Mr Gibb's position on the
OL,15,FBBC board.
OL,17,FLiberal Democrat leader Sir Ed Davey
OL,18,Fsaid Sir Robbie should be removed from
OL,19,Fthe board immediately.
