OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FIt follows claims to The Guardian that
OL,7,FMr Gibb 'lead the charge' in claims
OL,8,Fover systemic bias at the corporation
OL,10,FWriting in the newspaper, Davey said
OL,11,FMr Gibb should not have a say in
OL,12,Fchoosing the BBC's next director-
OL,13,Fgeneral as a member of the board.
OL,15,F"To ensure the BBC's independence,
OL,16,Fimpartiality and trust, Gibb should
OL,17,Fhave no role in appointing the new
OL,18,Fdirector general," he wrote.
