OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FWhen asked whether Robbie Gibb should
OL,7,Fbe on the BBC board due to his
OL,8,Fpolitical background, Swinney said, "
OL,9,FIn my opinion, no, he shouldn't,
OL,10,Fbecause I think it's important that
OL,11,Fthe BBC throughout its organisation is
OL,12,Fviewed to be impartial and
OL,13,Fauthoritative and dispassionate.
OL,15,F"And I think when it's got a figure
OL,16,Flike Robbie Gibb on its board, then I
OL,17,Fthink that undermines the authority
OL,18,Fand the impartiality of the BBC.
