OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FThe board is led by BBC chairman Samir
OL,7,FShah and consists of 10 non-executive
OL,8,Fmembers, including Shah and four
OL,9,Fexecutive members.
OL,11,FFour of the non-executive members are
OL,12,Fappointed as members for each of the
OL,13,FUK nations.
OL,15,FThe board is responsible for ensuring
OL,16,Fthe BBC delivers on its mission and
OL,17,Fpublic purposes.
