OL,3,CWho is Robbie Gibb and why do some
OL,4,Cwant him removed from the BBC board?
OL,6,FSpeaking to reporters on Monday, Ms
OL,7,FTurness rejected claims of
OL,8,Finstitutional bias at the BBC, adding
OL,9,F"that's why it's the world's most
OL,10,Ftrusted news provider."
OL,12,FAsked why mistakes were not dealt
OL,13,Fwith, including on Mr Trump, on
OL,14,Fantisemitism, and on women's rights,
OL,15,FMs Turness replied: "I'm sure that
OL,16,Fstory will emerge."
